* {{ill|lt=Sarutahiko|Q3090037|WD=Q3090037|lt=Sarutahiko-no-Mikoto|1=Sarutahiko Ōkami}}

=== Cultural properties ===
; Important Cultural Property (National designation)
* Honden - former honden of Kamigamo Shrine in Kyoto (early Edo period architecture, moved in 1865), three-bay nagare-zukuri, cypress-bark roof, designated April 30, 1921
* Wooden seated Yoshihiko-no-Mikoto statue (with two wooden seated attendant deity statues) - Heian period, wood

; City designated cultural property
* Mikoshi

